name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Yesterday, the White House confirmed that President Obama will meet with Pope Francis during his visit in September. Some experts are wondering if they'll discuss their disagreement over contraception. Then Joe Biden said, “I didn't even know they were dating.”

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Yeah, the president will meet with Pope Francis at the White House in September. The two will meet for about an hour or so, and then the Pope will spend the rest of the day hearing confessions from Secret Service agents.

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Oprah is auctioning off over a million dollars' worth of her belongings from her Chicago apartment. Or as she calls them, "her least favorite things."

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Willie Nelson is apparently developing his own brand of weed and bongs. Which I guess is like his version of Oprah's garage sale.
